version 0.5.1:
* Formatter is now more extensible through the use of engine registry
  - Out of the box, the gem will support 5 languages for the formatter (date and number/currency formatter),
    but developer can easily extend the formatter to different languages, see the files in 
    format_engine folder on how to write the language support.
* Updated the view_helper to better use default argument list.
* Updated gem loader file so it will dynamically load all .rb files
* Added example application
* Added multibyte support (requires unicodechars gem)
* Content files are now in YAML format
* Translator and formatter are now singleton objects
* README take 2
